# CCB Database Migration to OCI DBaaS
## Oracle Database Migration from On-Premises to OCI Database Service

### Project Overview
Migration of CCB (Core Application) Oracle database from on-premises RAC cluster to OCI DBaaS with Data Guard for high availability.

### Business Objectives
- **High Availability**: 99.95% database uptime
- **Performance**: Exadata performance benefits
- **Disaster Recovery**: RPO < 5 minutes, RTO < 1 hour
- **Cost Optimization**: 40% reduction vs on-premises

###  Database Architecture

#### Source Environment (On-Premises)
On-Premises Database:
├── Oracle RAC Cluster (2 nodes)
├── ASM Storage
├── Backup to Tape
└── Limited DR Capability
